{{Quote|Hello, good spacers. Paxtrell Snoygal is the moniker and I represent Cosmohaul Shipping. Today is your lucky day. I'm going to help you folks make your fortunes.|[[Paxtrell Snoygal]]|<ref name="Journal9">{{JournalCite|9|Droids Defiant}}</ref>}}
'''Cosmohaul Shipping''' was a cargo transportation company.<ref name="Journal9" />

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Cosmohaul Shipping appeared in "[[Droids Defiant]]," a [[Roleplaying game|roleplaying]] adventure written by [[Thomas Bowling]] and published in the [[February]] [[1996]] [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 9|ninth issue]] of [[West End Games]]' ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]'' magazine for use with ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]''.<ref name="Journal9" />

